Sixth round of mining rules: 
1. There is no upper limit on the number of mining pools for GOF mining. As long as a mining pool has more than 200,000 votes, it can become a mining pool and participate in mining; 
2. The sixth round of mining The amount is 60,000 GOF; 
3. The total amount of mining pools for each coin is ranked according to the voting rank, the first place accounts for 30% of the total, the second place 20%, the third place 15%, and the remaining pools divide the remaining 35 % GOF total, ie 21,000 GOF. However, starting from the fourth place, the total amount of each pool does not exceed 10%, which is 6,000 GOF. More than 10% will be reserved for the next round of mining pools  (Get GOF back to 10U!)

第六轮挖矿规则:1.GOF挖矿的矿池数量不设限制，只要某矿池投票票数超过20万，即可成为一个矿池，并参与挖矿；2.第六轮挖矿总量是6万个gof；3.每种币的矿池总量按名次排，第一名占30%总量，第二名20%，第三名15%，其余的矿池平分其余的35% GOF总量，即21,000 GOF。但从第四名矿池开始，每个矿池总量最高不超过百分之十，即6,000 GOF。超过百分之10的部分，留到下一轮矿池 （添加微信进群:18611371157，凝聚gof持有者所有力量，力推Gof回10U）
